title: Effect of laws, ordinances, and rules
context: ยง342F-20 Effect of laws, ordinances, and rules. Any county may adopt ordinances and rules governing any matter relating to excessive noise control as provided in section 46-17, and any conflict between state and county law shall be resolved as provided in section 46-17.
